waht is a keyword?
keywords is a reserved predefine words in javascript.
they have special meaning in javscript.
they cannot be as used variable name and function name or any other identfire


Eveent loop is a mechansim that make sure that the code run in the correct order.
event loop is responsible to exceuting the code and collecting the events.